    "multicolumn_qLqDh9": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_KqraYg": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "color_scheme": "",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "show_overlay_on_hover": false,
            "title": "Mongolian Cashmere",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_size_mobile": "h3--mobile",
            "text": "<p>Extremely soft to the touch, these plush cashmere rugs are simply bliss beneath your feet. Made with luxurious cashmere wool, this lustrous collection is available in both solid color shades and a variety of Moroccan lattice patterns.</p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "text_style_mobile": "body--mobile",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "shopify://collections/featured-collection",
            "show_link_as_button": false,
            "card_padding": 0.5
          }
        },
        "column_7PmAwR": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "show_overlay_on_hover": false,
            "title": "Dunes Wool & Silk Rug",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_size_mobile": "h3--mobile",
            "text": "<p>Made with wool and 50% silk, the rugs in the Dunes Wool & Silk RugCollection has a soft feel and lustrous shimmer. The striations in the rug give it texture and while offering an added level of dynamism within a space.</p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "text_style_mobile": "body--mobile",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "shopify://collections/featured-collection",
            "show_link_as_button": false,
            "card_padding": 0.5
          }
        },
        "column_aET3Qw": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "color_scheme": "",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "show_overlay_on_hover": false,
            "title": "Discovery Flatweaves",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_size_mobile": "h3--mobile",
            "text": "<p>Discovery Flatweaves offer traditional decorative designs in an ultra-fine kilim weave. Fully reversible, these rugs use production methods dating back to the Mughal dynasty such as 100% vegetable dyes and small batch dying, which give them their vibrant and natural colors.</p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "text_style_mobile": "body--mobile",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "shopify://collections/featured-collection",
            "show_link_as_button": false,
            "card_padding": 0.5
          }
