    "media_with_text_xAAgri": {
      "type": "media-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "content_wXtnbp": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "image_first": true,
            "video_url": "",
            "video_autoplay": false,
            "heading": "25 Years of Timeless Elegance – The Jewel Rug",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text": "<p>We are proud to celebrate the 25-year anniversary of our iconic <a href=\"https://samad.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=eeb16ae0730645685acdaf94e&id=dbaf4ab329&e=1b148ab8b7\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Jewel rug</strong></a> from the bestselling <a href=\"https://samad.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=eeb16ae0730645685acdaf94e&id=bf611d671b&e=1b148ab8b7\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Golden Age Collection</strong></a>. The first Jewel rug sold was in July 1999, and is still programed 25 years later – an unprecedented achievement in Samad’s 40-year history! </p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "mobile_text_style": "body--mobile",
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": "https://blog.samad.com/jewel-rug/",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "button_label_2": "",
            "button_link_2": "",
            "button_style_secondary_2": false,
            "box_color_scheme": "scheme-1",
            "desktop_content_position": "middle",
            "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
            "content_layout": "overlap",
            "mobile_content_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "content_8aNz7r": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "image_first": true,
            "video_url": "",
            "video_autoplay": false,
            "heading": "Luxury Pink Rugs for Modern Décor",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Luxury pink rugs are the perfect way to introduce a touch of elegance and playfulness into modern decor. From soft blush to bold fuchsia, pink rugs offer endless design possibilities to enhance any space. Integrating pink into modern decor, can help achieve a look that’s stylish, welcoming and full of life.</p>",
